                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold">Mission</h3>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">To help every team work better together. We build tools that remove friction, foster collaboration, and let people focus on what they do best.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-delay="100">
