                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold">Speed Over Perfection</h3>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Done is better than perfect. We ship early, learn fast, and iterate constantly. Our best features came from listening to real users.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-delay="200">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
              <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                <div class="bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-3 p-3 d-inline-flex mb-3">
                  <i class="bi bi-heart fs-3 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold">Users First</h3>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Every decision starts with the question: will this make our users lives easier? If not, we do not build it.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4" data-animate="fade-up">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
              <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                <div class="bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-3 p-3 d-inline-flex mb-3">
                  <i class="bi bi-transparency fs-3 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold">Radical Transparency</h3>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">We share our roadmap publicly, publish our uptime, and admit when we mess up. Trust is earned through honesty.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-delay="100">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
              <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                <div class="bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-3 p-3 d-inline-flex mb-3">
                  <i class="bi bi-people fs-3 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold">Inclusive by Design</h3>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Great products work for everyone. We prioritize accessibility, support multiple languages, and build for diverse teams.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-delay="200">
            <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
              <div class="card-body p-4 text-center">
                <div class="bg-primary bg-opacity-10 rounded-3 p-3 d-inline-flex mb-3">
                  <i class="bi bi-tree fs-3 text-primary"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="h5 fw-bold">Sustainable Growth</h3>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">We are bootstrapped and profitable. No vanity metrics, no growth hacks. Just steady progress on a product people love.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
